                    <p>Each way effectively sets the appropriate <code class="inline-code">Content-Type</code> header and properly formats the data for that data type.</p>
                    <h5 id="rendering-requests">Rendering Requests</h5>
                    <p>Client requests can be rendered out to a raw string:</p>
                    <pre><code class="language-php">use Pop\Http\Client;

