                    <h5 id="responses" class="mt-4">Responses</h5>
                    <p>Upon sending a request, the response object is automatically created and populated with the content from the raw response.</p>
                    <pre><code class="language-php">use Pop\Http\Client;

$response = Client::post('http://localhost/post', [
