                    <h5 id="handlers" class="mt-4">Handlers</h5>
                    <p>You can choose to use a different handler with the client object. The available handlers are:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-4">
                        <li class="mb-2 text-sm"><code class="inline-code">Pop\Http\Client\Handler\Curl</code><span class="text-sm"> - uses the PHP curl extension (default)</span></li>
                        <li class="mb-2 text-sm"><code class="inline-code">Pop\Http\Client\Handler\Stream</code><span class="text-sm"> - uses PHP stream functionality</span></li>
                        <li class="mb-2 text-sm"><code class="inline-code">Pop\Http\Client\Handler\CurlMulti</code><span class="text-sm"> - reserved for multiple parallel/concurrent requests at the same time</span></li>
                    </ul>
                    <pre><code class="language-php">use Pop\Http\Client;
