                    <p>The <code class="inline-code">catch()</code> and <code class="inline-code">finally()</code> methods also have the same <code class="inline-code">$resolve</code> force flag.</p>
                    <h5 id="forwarding">Forwarding</h5>
                    <p>You can chain multiple <code class="inline-code">then()</code> method calls together, which is sometimes called "forwarding" a promise.
                        The return of the first <code class="inline-code">then()</code> call needs to be another promise object.</p>
